Your indexer is ready! Pick how you'd like to run it:

  1. cd 'my-indexer' && pnpm test    # run the tests (recommended for AI)
  2. cd 'my-indexer' && pnpm dev     # run locally
  3. cd 'my-indexer' && pnpm start   # run in production
